name: AnimeHP
description:
This model is based on my Hodgepodge model. If you enjoy prompting on Hodgepodge, you will love the result of this model as well.

Do not try to get photorealistic images on this model, it is not for that. This model is for those who want to get high-quality graphics and images in anime style.

If you like the results of my work, feel free to like and stars. The model is free for anyone who wants to use it for personal purposes. I do not and will not take money for my work. Your reviews, stars and likes are the maximum reward I can count on.
